Practice Questions
Q1. Show all columns plus the previous Amount using LAG().

   SELECT *, 
         LAG(Amount) OVER (ORDER BY SaleID) AS PrevAmount 
   FROM Sales;

Q2. Show all columns plus the next Amount using LEAD().

   SELECT *, 
         LEAD(Amount) OVER (ORDER BY SaleID) AS NextAmount 
   FROM Sales;

Q3. Show both previous and next Amount in the same query.

   SELECT *, 
         LAG(Amount) OVER (ORDER BY SaleID), 
         LEAD(Amount) OVER (ORDER BY SaleID) 
   FROM Sales;

Q4. Show previous Month using LAG(Month).

   SELECT *, 
         LAG(Month) OVER (ORDER BY SaleID) AS PrevMonth 
   FROM Sales;

Q5. Show next Month using LEAD(Month).

   SELECT *, 
         LEAD(Month) OVER (ORDER BY SaleID) AS NextMonth 
   FROM Sales;
